org.jamplate.impl.analyzer

Class ConditionTransformAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamplate.impl.analyzer.ConditionTransformAnalyzer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Analyzer

    public class ConditionTransformAnalyzer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Analyzer
    An analyzer that transforms trees that has a kind equal to a pre-specified kind to another pre-specified kind if a pre-specified predicate returned true.
